export default function calculateTime(t,l){try{let e=[t,l],o=0;for(let t of e){let[l,e,a]=t.split(":").map(parseFloat);o+=3600*l,o+=60*e,o+=a||0}let a=Math.floor(o/3600);o-=3600*a;let r=Math.floor(o/60);return o-=60*r,o<=9&&(o="0"+o),r<=9&&(r="0"+r),a<=9&&(a="0"+a),`${a}:${r}:${o}`}catch(t){throw t}}